## 7. Count Vowels and Consonants

```java
public static void countVowelConsonant(String s) {
    s = s.toLowerCase();
    String vowels = "aeiou";
    int vc = 0, cc = 0;

    for (char c : s.toCharArray()) {
        if (Character.isLetter(c)) {
            if (vowels.indexOf(c) != -1) vc++;
            else cc++;
        }
    }
    System.out.println("Vowels: " + vc + ", Consonants: " + cc);
}

// Using Set (faster lookup)
public static void countVowelConsonantSet(String s) {
    Set<Character> vowelSet = Set.of('a','e','i','o','u','A','E','I','O','U');
    int vowels = 0, consonants = 0;

    for (char c : s.toCharArray()) {
        if (Character.isLetter(c)) {
            if (vowelSet.contains(c)) vowels++;
            else consonants++;
        }
    }
}
```

