## 12. Word Frequency Count

```java
// "hello world hello java" → {hello=2, world=1, java=1}
public static Map<String, Integer> wordFrequency(String sentence) {
    Map<String, Integer> freq = new LinkedHashMap<>();
    for (String word : sentence.split("\\s+")) {
        freq.merge(word.toLowerCase(), 1, Integer::sum);
    }
    return freq;
}

// Top K frequent words
public static List<String> topKWords(String sentence, int k) {
    Map<String, Integer> freq = wordFrequency(sentence);

    // Bucket by frequency
    List<String>[] bucket = new List[sentence.split("\\s+").length + 1];
    for (Map.Entry<String, Integer> e : freq.entrySet()) {
        int f = e.getValue();
        if (bucket[f] == null) bucket[f] = new ArrayList<>();
        bucket[f].add(e.getKey());
    }

    List<String> result = new ArrayList<>();
    for (int i = bucket.length - 1; i >= 0 && result.size() < k; i--) {
        if (bucket[i] != null) {
            Collections.sort(bucket[i]); // alphabetical tiebreak
            result.addAll(bucket[i]);
        }
    }
    return result.subList(0, Math.min(k, result.size()));
}
```

